&lt;p>That&amp;rsquo;s why I&amp;rsquo;m giving you this solution. For example with SSH, if I want to restart it:&lt;/p>



 
 
 

 
 
 
 

 

 &lt;div class="prism-codeblock ">
 &lt;pre id="51ce67d" class="language-bash ">
 &lt;code>kill -HUP `cat /var/run/sshd.pid`&lt;/code>
 &lt;/pre>
 &lt;/div>
&lt;p>It&amp;rsquo;s as simple as that. Now you can manually restart it:&lt;/p>



 
 
 

 
 
 
 

 

 &lt;div class="prism-codeblock ">
 &lt;pre id="dcdf609" class="language-bash ">
 &lt;code>/usr/sbin/sshd&lt;/code>
 &lt;/pre>
 &lt;/div></description></item></channel></rss>